and Hummels, Cameron and Kritsuk, Alexei G and Tasker,
Elizabeth and Skory, Stephen and Simpson, Christine M and
Hahn, Oliver and Oishi, Jeffrey S and So, Geoffrey C and
Zhao, Fen and Cen, Renyue and Li, Yuan},
 eprint = {1307.2265},
 keywords = {Authorship},
 month = {July},
